{"tid":1647753,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典網絡保安科技公司   捐 500 支保安鎖匙予民間記者抗爭者","createTime":"2019-10-12T01:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T06:45:04.000Z","uid":273929,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e6968b68572554e2879bee8a108b035e04cc963f","tid":1647753,"uid":273929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/10/yubico-donates-500-yubikey-to-hk-reporters-protestors/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F10%2Fyubico-donates-500-yubikey-to-hk-reporters-protestors%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=95414b08\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/10/yubico-donates-500-yubikey-to-hk-reporters-protestors/tech-secure/</a><br />\n<br />\n由 6 月至今還未平息的香港反送中運動，引起的討論越來越多，當中不少涉及警方取用被捕人士和抗爭者電腦的問題。有網民於 8 月聯絡瑞典網絡保安公司 Yubico 解釋事件，最後獲得對方捐贈 500 條 Yubikey 網絡保安鎖匙，給予民間記者和抗爭者，加強他們的電腦保安。<br />\nYubikey 是硬件二步認證裝置，簡單來說就是一條安全金鑰，在用戶利用瀏覽器登入帳戶時，除了平時需要輸入密碼，還要同時將 Yubikey 插入電腦方可以進入帳戶。沒有 Yubikey 作為硬件二步認證，任何人都無法登入帳號。現時 Yubikey 支援的網絡服務包括 Google、Facebook、Instagram 等，同時支援 Windows 和 macOS 系統。<br />\nYubikey 被網絡保安專家譽為「unhackable」，就連 Google 亦要求旗下員工使用 Yubikey 進行二步認證，以避免國家級黑客可以繞過 SMS 短訊或 OTP 單次使用密碼認證。Yubico 今次向香港捐贈的是基本版，沒有 NFC 的 Security Key by Yubico，但已經具備基本的二步認證功能。負責聯絡和統籌的陳婉容在 Facebook 表示，他們會循不同途徑將 Yubikey 派發予民間記者和抗爭者。"},{"pid":"4fb292362a85e4c8d6ecc407da1d4d3105d3d17d","tid":1647753,"uid":178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:41:01.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa910852620812235fbf50930edefd1761ea58d1","tid":1647753,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code> <br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"6d83660bce6e9e9c04575a6a66e86ea8c23b3384","tid":1647753,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"